{
  "chapter": 41,
  "chapter_summary": "本章中，李寻欢与郭嵩阳发现阿飞已被林仙儿带走，通过屋中秘道追踪至小楼。在小楼中遇到穿红衣服的小姑娘，从小姑娘处得知一名大胡子男人曾来寻找李寻欢并留下一封信。信竟是上官金虹所写，约李寻欢十月初一于山谷飞泉之下相会。李寻欢隐瞒信的内容，与小姑娘言语周旋，决定暂留小楼。郭嵩阳亦留下作伴。本章展现了林仙儿狡兔三窟之能，以及李寻欢面对上官金虹挑战时的从容与深沉。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说阿飞是你的好朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你却不知道他已走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "也许，他遇着了什么意外，也许……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "也许是因为他比较听女人的话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他们已在这里住了很久？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "快两年了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但两年以前，她已约我在那小楼上见过面了，这地方说不定就是她的老窝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "狡兔三窟，她的窝必定不止这一处。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "可惜我却只知道这一处。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我出来的时候，她留在楼上，现在她却已回来过，而且已经将阿飞带走了，我们在路上竟未发现她的踪迹……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "这只不过因为她走的是另外一条路。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "另外一条路，这里四面环山，难道还有什么捷径？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "捷径也许就在山腹里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "以你看，这条路的出口是在什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "那小楼上的床下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我也是这么想……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "下了这张床，就上那张床，她做事倒真不肯浪费时间。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "她的约会很忙，时间自然宝贵得很。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来你们是认得的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "这里只剩下你一个人了？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "你这么凶干什么？每次你来的时候，替你铺床的是我，替你收被的也是我，你难道已忘了么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你就是李探花？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你真的就是那大名鼎鼎的小李探花李寻欢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我也不是不相信，只不过有些想不到而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "想不到什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "别人都说李寻欢不但武功最高，人也最精明，最能干，我实在没有想到你也会被人骗，上人的当。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "上次我骗了你，真抱歉得很。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "没关系，偶尔被小孩子骗一次，也是件很开心的事，我自从被你骗过一次后，就觉得自己好像年轻多了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我看你就算没有被我骗，本来也年轻得很，若是再被我骗几次，只怕就要变成小孩子了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我以后一定会很小心……四十岁的小孩子，岂非要被人当做妖怪了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你只管放心，上次我骗了你，因为你还是个陌生人，奶奶从小就告诉我，千万不能对陌生人说老实话，否则也许就会被人拐走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "现在呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "现在我们已认识，我自然不会再骗你。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "那么，我问你，你刚刚可曾看到有人从这里出来么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但我却看到有人从外面进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "是个男人，我不认识他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "除了你之外，我认得的男人并不多。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "他是来干什么的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "那人长得很凶狠，一嘴大胡子，脸上还有个刀疤，一走进来就问我，认不认识李寻欢？李寻欢会不会来？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "因为我不认得他，所以就故意骗他，说我认得你，你马上就会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "那么他说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他就交给我一封信，要我转交给你，还说一定要我交给你本人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你就收下了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我当然收下了……我若不收下，谎话岂非就要被揭穿了么？那人凶得很，若知道我在说谎，不打破我的头才怪。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "女孩子的头若被打破，一定疼得很，你说是不是？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "男孩子的头若被打破，也疼得很的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "信上写的是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "没有什么。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "瞧你笑得这么开心，这封信只怕是女人写给你的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "猜对了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她是不是想约你见面？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "又猜对了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "早知是女人写的信，我才不交给你哩。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "你若不交给我，她一定会很伤心的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她是个怎么样的人？漂不漂亮？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "当然漂亮，否则我早就将这封信甩到一边去了，女人长得丑，简直比男人生得笨还要可怕。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她有多大年龄？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "年纪也不大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "她至少比我大得多了吧？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "幸好她比你大，否则我就只好收她做干女儿了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "既然有这么样一位漂亮的老太婆约你，你为什么还不赶快去见她，还待在这里干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "做主人的，怎么可以赶客人走？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我就算不赶你，反正也是要走的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我若不走呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你若不走，我这做主人的当然要想法子招待你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "当然是真的，我虽然不大方，可也不是小气鬼，你若要在这里呆十天，我就招待你十天，你若要在这里呆一辈子，我也……也不会赶你走的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "好，那么我就留在这里……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你说的是真话？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "当然是真的，难得遇到你这么好的主人，我怎么会走呢？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我知道你喜欢喝酒，我这就去替你准备，这地方别的没有，酒却多得很……多得可以淹死你。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "除了酒之外，我还要几块木头，越硬越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "木头？要木头干什么？难道你要用木头来下酒？你的牙齿倒真不错。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但你既然要木头，我就替你去拿木头来，无论你想要什么，就算想要天上的月亮，我也会去替你搬梯子的。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "我不吃木头，我吃蛋，无论是鸡蛋、鸭蛋、皮蛋、咸蛋，只要是蛋就可以，越多越好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "text": "你也要留在这里？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_song_yang",
      "speaker_name": "郭嵩阳",
      "listener": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "text": "难得遇到你这么好的主人，我怎么肯走呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_gu_niang",
      "speaker_name": "小姑娘",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这世上不识相的人倒真不少，什么事不好做，为什么偏偏要煞别人的风景呢……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 41,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    }
  ],
